divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting outside watching the sky and saw a star that didn't belong in the sky. When I looked at it I saw that it was moving,north to south. It moved very slow and after a couple of minutes it made a 110 degree turn to the east, it stopped, started to pulsate and then made a 90 degree turn to the south and increased it's speed to disappear after a short while.The event took about 30 minutes to complete.
